Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.65,0:01:02.70,OPch,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}記憶如花瓣般衰敗消散
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.87,0:01:14.38,OPch,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(150,150)}觸碰的瞬間 破碎散落
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.97,0:01:22.35,OPch,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(150,150)}帶我走吧!
